Category

public enum Category

Represents the five categories of HTTP response codes.

  • Informational

    Indicates an informational (1xx) response, possibly pending further information.

    Declaration

    Swift

    case Informational
  • Success

    Indicates an successful (2xx) response.

    Declaration

    Swift

    case Success
  • Redirection

    Indicates a redirect (3xx) response.

    Declaration

    Swift

    case Redirection
  • ClientError

    Indicates a client error (4xx) response.

    Declaration

    Swift

    case ClientError
  • ServerError

    Indicates a server error (5xx) response, or a response with an error code not falling into one of the ranges above.

    Declaration

    Swift

    case ServerError
